@no_majority
title: There is no clear governing majority.
view-if: vf_seats_vienna <= 50 and oclk_seats_vienna <= 50

The previous coalition continues to govern as a minority government.



@vf_majority
title: The <span style="color: #ED2939;">**VF**</span> forms a majority government.
subtitle: <span style="color: #ED2939;">**VF**</span> ([+ vf_wl +]%)
view-if: vf_seats_vienna > 50
on-arrival: {!
Q.vienna_oclk = 0;
Q.vienna_vf = 1;

Q.in_vf_majority_vienna = 1;
Q.in_oclk_majority_vienna = 0;
!}

